'''奧-{}-克蘭'''（{{lang-en|Oakland}}；意為“橡樹之地”）是[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]北部[[舊金山灣|舊金山灣]]沿岸的主要城市，也是[[阿拉米達縣_(加利福尼亞州)|阿拉米達縣]]縣治所在。俗稱「'''歐克城'''」（Oaktown），當地華人及粵語社群則常稱「'''屋-{}-崙'''」。其與[[柏克萊|柏克萊]]位於[[舊金山灣區|舊金山灣區]]東邊，此區域也稱為「{{Link-en|舊金山東灣|East Bay (San Francisco Bay Area)|東灣}}」。

奧克蘭建於1852年，早期居民為在[[舊金山|舊金山]]上班的藍領階級。它的北方是著名[[柏克萊加州大學|柏克萊加州大學]]所在地；[[舊金山-歐克蘭海灣大橋|舊金山-歐克蘭海灣大橋]]連接的舊金山位於其西邊；西南方有[[阿拉米達|阿拉米達]]島，南邊以聖利安卓為鄰。奧克蘭行政區內還有一個富裕的獨立城鎮[[皮蒙特_(加利福尼亚州)|皮蒙特]]（Piedmont）。

根據[[美國人口調查局|美國人口調查局]]2006年统計，歐克蘭是舊金山灣區第三大城市，人口僅次於舊金山及[[聖荷西_(美國加州)|聖荷西]]，共有415,492人。2008年國會調查報告顯示歐克蘭在全美最危險的城市中排行第五，在加州所有城市中，與北邊的[[列治文_(加利福尼亞州)|列治文]]和南加州的[[康普顿_(加利福尼亚州)|康普顿]]同等危險。

[[奧克蘭港_(美國)|歐克蘭港]]是美國西海岸三大主要商港之一。[[奧克蘭國際機場_(美國)|歐克蘭國際機場]]是[[廉價航空公司|廉價航空公司]]（主要是[[西南航空|西南航空]]和[[捷藍航空|捷藍航空]]）旅客往來舊金山地區的主要門户。奧克蘭也是北加州列車運輸中心，貨運經奧克蘭港卸貨後由列車運往美西各地。

做為舊金山的重要[[衛星城市|衛星城市]]，奧克蘭由於地價較一水之隔的舊金山便宜，許多企業總部坐落於此，如全美最大的連鎖醫院{{link-en|凱薩醫療機構|Kaiser Permanente}}、[[Ask.com|Ask.com]]、{{link-en|高樂氏|Clorox|Clorox漂白水}}、[[醉爾斯冰淇淋|醉爾斯冰淇淋]]、[[哈根達斯|哈根達斯冰淇淋]]、[[Pandora电台|潘朵拉線上音樂]]、旅遊書出版社[[寂寞星球|寂寞星球]]等。

== 歷史 ==
=== Ohlone ===
最早在今天奧克蘭的位置定居的是一個叫做Huchiun的印第安部族，集中住在今[[梅里特湖|梅里特湖]]（Lake Merritt）一帶<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nativecc.com/OhloneTribalMap.html/ |title=Ohlone Tribal Regions Map |accessdate=April 15, 2007 |last=Milliken |first=Randall |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070813110544/http://www.nativecc.com/OhloneTribalMap.html/ |archivedate=2007年8月13日 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

=== 西班牙殖民時期 ===
西班牙征服者（[[征服者|Conquistadors]]）于1772年以[[西班牙|西班牙]]國王名義佔領了奧克蘭一帶的土地。十九世紀初，西班牙國王將這塊土地賜予了一個叫做{{tsl|en|Luís María Peralta||Peralta}}的軍人在這裡開農場謀生（獨立後管理加州的[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]政府沒有反對Peralta的業權）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://oakland-california.co.tv/ |title=Oakland-california.co.tv |publisher=Oakland-california.co.tv |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |archive-date=2011-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110411053608/http://oakland-california.co.tv/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。農場就叫做{{tsl|en|Rancho San Antonio|}}。農場裏面有一排橡樹由今下城的位置生到出去今日阿拉米達市的位置。Peralta叫這裡為Ecinal，即橡樹園的西班牙文。Peralta將這塊地分給他四個孩子，當中獲得大部份土地的Antonion和Vincent將這塊地開放給搬到這裡的居民和商人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oaklandcaliforniarealestate.biz/History.asp |title=Oaklandcaliforniarealestate.biz |publisher=Oaklandcaliforniarealestate.biz |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324183040/http://www.oaklandcaliforniarealestate.biz/History.asp |archivedate=2012年3月24日 }}</ref>。

=== 一八五零年至一九零零年 ===
[[美墨戰爭|美墨戰爭]]中戰敗方墨西哥將包括奧克蘭在內的大半江山給予了[[美國|美國]]政府<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ourdocuments.gov/doc.php?flash=true&doc=26|title=Treaty of Guadalupe Hidalgo|publisher=ourdocuments.gov|accessdate=June 27, 2007|archive-date=2007-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070715115058/http://www.ourdocuments.gov/doc.php?flash=true&doc=26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿拉米達縣成立前，這裡有個徙置區叫做Contra Costa（意思是「彼岸」）。1852年加州議會通過法案，允許奧克蘭正式建市<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.texasranger.org/halloffame/Hays_John.htm |title=Texas Ranger Hays |publisher=Texasranger.org |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |archive-date=2018-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180211045905/http://www.texasranger.org/halloffame/Hays_John.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

自此奧克蘭獲得大力發展。鐵路在19世紀60年代末通車後，奧克蘭就建造了主要的鐵路總站。1868年，[[中央太平洋公司|中央太平洋公司]]（Central Pacific）在奧克蘭建造了一個「[[大碼頭|大碼頭]]」，即今奧克蘭海港碼頭（[[奧克蘭港_(美國)|奧克蘭港]]）。海港碼頭就成了跨大陸鐵路（[[横贯大陆铁路|横贯大陆铁路]]）和其他地區性鐵路的總站。而當年還沒有海灣大橋，因此渡輪是東灣居民來往三藩市的重要交通工具<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.welcomeaboard.com/ |title=See |publisher=Welcomeaboard.com |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |archive-date=2012-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120428163744/http://www.welcomeaboard.com/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

今日的人工湖[[梅里特湖|梅里特湖]]當年只是一片濕地。1870年，當時的市長 Samuel Merritt 下令建造美麗湖。建造初期保留周圍的濕地作為野生動物保育區，但持續有人在這裡建造房屋令濕地消失。大約在1915年，美麗湖周邊變成了今日的面貌，成為了一個被公園圍住的湖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tps.cr.nps.gov/nhl/detail.cfm?ResourceId=112&ResourceType=Site|title=Lake Merritt Wild Duck Refuge|date=2007-09-28|work=National Historic Landmark summary listing|publisher=National Park Service|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219191450/http://tps.cr.nps.gov/nhl/detail.cfm?ResourceId=112&ResourceType=Site|archivedate=2012-02-19|access-date=2013-07-11}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.oaklandnet.com/parks/customerservice/faq.asp?ans=9 |title=City of Oakland Parks and Recreation |access-date=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2008-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081114142021/http://www.oaklandnet.com/parks/customerservice/faq.asp?ans=9 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.oaklandheritage.org/OHA25.pdf |title=Project1<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2006-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060819034054/http://www.oaklandheritage.org/OHA25.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.oaklandnet.com/parks/parks/lakemerritt_wildlifesanctuary.asp |title=Lake Merritt - Wildlife Sanctuary<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2006-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060129224827/http://www.oaklandnet.com/parks/parks/lakemerritt_wildlifesanctuary.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Richard Carleton Hacker, Special to The Chronicle |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/chronicle/a/2004/11/11/WIG619OSAL1.DTL |title=SF Gate. ''Trader Vic put mai tai on the lips of millions'' Richard Carleton Hacker, Special to The Chronicle. November 11, 2004 |work=San Francisco Chronicle |date=November 11, 2004 |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |archive-date=2006-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060523033819/http://sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fchronicle%2Fa%2F2004%2F11%2F11%2FWIG619OSAL1.DTL |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cshouse.org/ |title=Welcome to the Camron-Stanford House web site<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227090701/https://cshouse.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://clevelandcascade.org/ |title=Oakland's Cleveland Cascade<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2011-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110627075520/http://www.clevelandcascade.org/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scc.ca.gov/sccbb/0610bb/1006Board04_Lake_Merritt_Bird_Islands.pdf |title=Project Name<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2007-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070723145040/http://www.scc.ca.gov/sccbb/0610bb/1006Board04_Lake_Merritt_Bird_Islands.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

十九世紀後期，奧克蘭有多條來往其他城市的公共交通路線。1891年來往奧克蘭和柏克萊的電動公車開始營運，另外多條馬車和巴士路線組成一個所謂的{{tsl|en|Key System|}}，即今日{{tsl|en|AC Transit|}}前身。

=== 1900年代至第二次世界大戰 ===
由於人口日漸增加，奧克蘭市漸漸吞併附近的農莊和小鎮，例如它東面的[[阿拉米達縣|阿拉米達縣]]就變成現在的東奧克蘭。1906年，三藩市因地震受到破壞，大量居民搬家去奧克蘭。

==== 航空業 ====
[[File:Oakland_Rickenbacker-Acosta_1920.jpg|thumb]]

1909年9月21日，中國飛機工程師[[馮如|馮如]]（1884年1月12日-1912年8月25日）在現在{{tsl|en|Laney College|}}的位置成功試飛自製[[飛機|飛機]]，成為史上第一個中國飛行員。

1920年8月9日，試驗性質的航空郵政（{{tsl|en|Airmails of the United States#Transcontinental Air Mail|}}）由奧克蘭首次試飛<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.centennialofflight.gov/essay/Government_Role/1918-1924/POL3.htm |title=U.S. Centennial of Flight Commission. ''The U.S. Post Office Flies the Mail, 1918–1924'' |publisher=Centennialofflight.gov |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106112000/http://www.centennialofflight.gov/essay/Government_Role/1918-1924/POL3.htm |archivedate=2012年1月6日 }}</ref>。

1927年9月17日，著名飛行員[[查爾斯·林德伯格|查爾斯·林德伯格]]（Charles Lindbergh）主持開幕儀式，[[奧克蘭國際機場_(美國)|奧克蘭國際機場]]開始運作<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.westernaerospacemuseum.org/oakland/oaklandairport.html |title=Western Aerospace Museum. Oakland Airport Timeline. |accessdate=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2015-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016081833/http://www.westernaerospacemuseum.org/oakland/oaklandairport.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Monday, Aug. 29, 1927 |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,723051,00.html |title=TIME magazine, August 29, 1927. ''Dole Race'' |work=Time |date=August 29, 1927 |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |archive-date=2013-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130827053103/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,723051,00.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://history.sandiego.edu/gen/filmnotes/hellsangels.html |title=History Department at the [[University_of_San_Diego|University of San Diego]]. Film notes. ''Hell's Angels'' |access-date=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2007-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070210155713/http://history.sandiego.edu/gen/filmnotes/hellsangels.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1937年5月21號，傳奇女飛行員[[愛蜜莉亞·厄爾哈特|愛蜜莉亞·厄爾哈特]]（Amelia Mary Earhart）從奧克蘭起飛，開始了她人生最後一次飛行。

==== 汽車及其他工業發展 ====
到了20世紀20年代，已經有眾多工業家在奧克蘭開辦了工廠<ref>{{cite web |url=http://content.cdlib.org/ark:/13030/kt7199q9d0/ |title=Photo collection: ''New or greatly enlarged industrial establishments of Oakland and East Bay cities.'' by Oakland (Calif.) Chamber of Commerce. ca. 1917. Oakland Public Library, Oakland History Room |publisher=Content.cdlib.org |date=February 24, 2007 |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723161041/http://content.cdlib.org/ark:/13030/kt7199q9d0/ |archive-date=2013-07-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。1916年，[[通用汽車|通用汽車]]（General Motors）在奧克蘭開辦了一條[[雪佛蘭|雪佛蘭]]（Chevrolet）生產線。到1929年，[[佳士拿|佳士拿]]（Chrysler）也在奧克蘭開了生產線，奧克蘭被譽為「西岸的底特律」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oaklandhistory.com/files/chev.html |title=Oakland History Room. 1917 promotional photograph of a day's output at the Chevrolet factory |publisher=Oaklandhistory.com |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323180032/http://www.oaklandhistory.com/files/chev.html |archive-date=2012-03-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lincolnhighwayassoc.org/ca/traveler/2001-09/highway_nostalgia.html |title=The Traveler: The Newsletter of the Lincoln Highway Association—California Chapter. Fall 2001. Wes Hammond. ''Highway Nostalgia. Manufacturing Trucks Adjacent to the Lincoln Highway: Fageol Truck and Coach Company. Oakland, California, 1916–1938'' |publisher=Lincolnhighwayassoc.org |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319152907/http://www.lincolnhighwayassoc.org/ca/traveler/2001-09/highway_nostalgia.html |archive-date=2012-03-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://vintagetractors.com/Fageol.html |title=Vintage Tractors. ''Fageol'' |publisher=Vintagetractors.com |date=January 7, 1919 |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609092714/http://vintagetractors.com/Fageol.html |archive-date=2012-06-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=World History of the Automobile |last=Eckermann |first=Eric |coauthors=Peter L. Albrecht |year=2001 |publisher=SAE International |isbn=0-7680-0800-X |page=129 |url=http://books.google.com/?id=yLZeQwqNmdgC }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.durantcars.com/basics/history.shtml |title=Durant Cars. ''History'' |publisher=Durantcars.com |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310224217/http://www.durantcars.com/basics/history.shtml |archivedate=2012年3月10日 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://clubs.hemmings.com/clubsites/durant/Additions/Oakland-tour/OAK-TOUR.htm |title=Durant Motors Automobile Club. ''Durant Motor Company of California welcomes you''; Factory tour flyer |access-date=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2003-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030302172127/http://clubs.hemmings.com/clubsites/durant/Additions/Oakland-tour/OAK-TOUR.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.newspaperarchive.com/LandingPage.aspx?type=glp&search=oakland%20history%20eastmont%20automobile%20factory&img=\\na0037\6774012\31255565.html |title=Oakland Tribune, May 5, 1929. ''Chrysler plant'' |publisher=Newspaperarchive.com |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |archive-date=2012-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118133457/http://www.newspaperarchive.com/LandingPage.aspx?type=glp&search=oakland%20history%20eastmont%20automobile%20factory&img=%5C%5Cna0037%5C6774012%5C31255565.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1929年，[[醉爾斯冰淇淋|醉爾斯冰淇淋]]雪糕在奧克蘭首次推出「石板街」（Rocky Road）雪糕<ref>{{cite web |title=Dreyer's History |format=PDF |url=http://www.dreyersinc.com/about/WebHistory.pdf |accessdate=April 5, 2006 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ATUI4Sdy?url=http://web.archive.org/web/20060312093431/http://www.dreyersinc.com/about/WebHistory.pdf |archive-date=2012-09-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

1936年11月12日，[[舊金山-奧克蘭海灣大橋|海灣大橋]]通車，當時上層橋面行駛汽車而下層橋面做鐵路用。

=== 第二次世界大戰 ===
[[二次大戰|二次大戰]]期間，整個東灣都投入和戰爭有關的業務。例如凱撒船塢（Kaiser Shipyards）和摩亞旱塢（Moore Dry Dock Company）。另外，罐頭食品需求龐大，所以有不少食品廠在這裡開廠，例如地們（Del Monte）生產商The Oakland Preserving Company<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://collections.museumca.org/qtvr_panos/qtvr7.html |title=Oakland Museum of California. Panoramic photo of H.G. Prince employees in Fruitvale in 1918 |access-date=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2003-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030626011504/http://collections.museumca.org/qtvr_panos/qtvr7.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

大戰不只為奧克蘭帶來了商家，同時亦吸引了全國各地的勞工；不過帶來生產力之餘亦帶來當時南部州份的[[種族隔離主義|種族隔離主義]]，使各種族關係日趨惡化<ref name="sfgate.com">{{cite news | url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2007/09/26/MNFUSA80E.DTL&hw=Betty+Reid+Soskin&sn=003&sc=552 | title=WWII meant opportunity for many women, oppression for others | first=Carolyne | last=Zinko | date=September 26, 2007 | work=The San Francisco Chronicle | accessdate=2021-09-04 | archive-date=2008-10-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081024034308/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2007%2F09%2F26%2FMNFUSA80E.DTL&hw=Betty+Reid+Soskin&sn=003&sc=552 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Arroyo>Arroyo, Cuahutémoc (Faculty Mentor: Professor {{tsl|en|Leon F. Litwack|}}). [http://www.ferris.edu/jimcrow/links/misclink/shipyards.htm ''"Jim Crow" Shipyards''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ferris.edu/jimcrow/links/misclink/shipyards.htm |date=20210206053024 }}: Black Labor and Race Relations in East Bay Shipyards During World War II. The Berkeley McNair Journal, The [[加州大學柏克萊分校|加州大學柏克萊分校]] [http://www-mcnair.berkeley.edu/McNair.html McNair Scholars Program] {{Wayback|url=http://www-mcnair.berkeley.edu/McNair.html |date=20071012192855 }}. Accessed from [http://www.ferris.edu/jimcrow/ Jim Crow Museum] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ferris.edu/jimcrow/ |date=20210307125026 }} of Racist Memorabilia at [[Ferris_State_University|Ferris State University]] on August 19, 2007</ref><ref name=Arroyo/>。

=== 戰後 ===
戰後，因為造船業同軍事工業停辦，所以就業機會大減，不少人因為這種原因選擇離開奧克蘭搬去附近的城市<ref name="INSIDE THE PANTHER REVOLUTION   p. 302">Inside the Panther Revolution, Robyn Cean Spencer, Chapter 13, p. 302</ref>。人是少了，但奧克蘭的種族問題就加劇了<ref name=cityjournal>{{cite web |url=http://www.city-journal.org/html/9_4_a2.html |title=Jerry Brown’s No-Nonsense New Age for Oakland. |publisher=City Journal |date=Autumn 1999 |author=Heather Mac Donald |accessdate=August 8, 2008 |authorlink=Heather Mac Donald |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080827074841/http://www.city-journal.org/html/9_4_a2.html |archive-date=2008-08-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://libcom.org/library/oakland-general-strike-stan-weir |title=1946: The Oakland General Strike |first=Stan |last=Weir |publisher=libcom.org |date=November 22, 2005 |accessdate=December 31, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111230100145/http://libcom.org/library/oakland-general-strike-stan-weir |archive-date=2011-12-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

四五十年代起，[[奧克蘭警察局|奧克蘭警察局]]（Oakland Police Department，OPD）顧請一批從[[美國深南部|南部]]來的警員，他們引入他們家鄉的一套來這裡執法，引發不少種族衝突<ref>Insie the Panther Revolution, Robyn Cean Spencer, Chapter 13, p. 303, "...Much of the city's police force had been recruited from the Deep South, and police officers frequently held racist attitudes."</ref>。

截至1966年，奧克蘭警察局中661個警員當中只有16個是黑人<ref name="INSIDE THE PANTHER REVOLUTION p. 302"/>。全國各地一連串警員打黑人事件後，{{tsl|en|Merritt College|}} 學生 {{tsl|en|Huey Newton|}} 于1966年10月在奧克蘭組織了「[[黑豹黨|黑豹黨]]」（Panther Party，簡稱 BPP）宣稱以武力自衛<ref>Up Against the Wall, Curtis Austin, pp. 30–47</ref>。另外，「[[地獄天使_(幫會)|地獄天使]]」電單車會開始由純粹電單車聯誼組織演變成[[飛車黨|飛車黨]]再演變成犯罪組織<ref name="doj-gangunit">{{cite web|url=http://www.justice.gov/criminal/gangunit/gangs/motorcycle.html|title=Motorcycle gangs|work=US Department of Justice|accessdate=January 23, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100210150226/http://www.justice.gov/criminal/gangunit/gangs/motorcycle.html|archivedate=2010年2月10日}}</ref><ref name="oc-ca">{{cite web|url=http://ag.ca.gov/publications/org_crime.pdf|title=Organized crime in California|last=Lockyer|first=Bill|year=2003|work={{tsl|en|California Department of Justice|加州司法部}}|accessdate=January 23, 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100129021517/http://ag.ca.gov/publications/org_crime.pdf|archive-date=2010-01-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。同一時期，奧克蘭市開始要面對毒品氾濫、[[黑社會|黑社會]]及暴力罪案等等一大堆以前並不存在的問題<ref>{{cite web |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=iuCKT-Gz5GcC&pg=PA41&lpg=PA41&dq=CRACK:+INNER+CITY+DECAY+IN+AMERICA&source=bl&ots=HHq4m1as-e&sig=d1xVxb4x-ZcEB78UXZPcZhy08ZE&hl=en&sa=X&ei=agvZT7rBG6mwiQf6rtmCAw&sqi=2&ved=0CFQQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=CRACK%3A%20INNER%20CITY%20DECAY%20IN%20AMERICA&f=false |title=Crack In America: Demon Drugs and Social Justice - Craig Reinarman, Harry Gene Levine - Google Books |publisher=Books.google.com |date= |accessdate=2012-07-24 |archive-date=2013-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724043557/http://books.google.com/books?id=iuCKT-Gz5GcC&pg=PA41&lpg=PA41&dq=CRACK:+INNER+CITY+DECAY+IN+AMERICA&source=bl&ots=HHq4m1as-e&sig=d1xVxb4x-ZcEB78UXZPcZhy08ZE&hl=en&sa=X&ei=agvZT7rBG6mwiQf6rtmCAw&sqi=2&ved=0CFQQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=CRACK%3A%20INNER%20CITY%20DECAY%20IN%20AMERICA&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 一九八零年代及其後 ===
自八十年代起，越來越多拉丁美裔移民搬入奧克蘭（尤其在{{tsl|en|Fruitvale, Oakland, California||Fruitvale}}區一帶）。這個區是奧克蘭舊區之一，原屬Peralta家族，所以比較吸引那些講西班牙語的拉丁美裔移民。

1989年10月17日，[[1989年洛马普列塔地震|1989年洛马普列塔地震]]震垮了一段架空的行車天橋，造成四十二人死亡。地震亦導致部份建築物損毀，包括海灣大橋。

1991年10月20日，{{tsl|en|1991 Oakland firestorm|1991年奧克蘭山火}}燒毀了大約六平方公里土地和約四千間屋，造成一百五十人受傷，二十五人死亡；經濟損失約十五億美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ktvu.com/news/news/disasters/some-faults-revealed-firestorm-remain-uncorrected/nFR7N/ |title=Some faults revealed by firestorm remain uncorrected |publisher=www.ktvu.com |date= |accessdate=2012-07-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120122005103/http://www.ktvu.com/news/news/disasters/some-faults-revealed-firestorm-remain-uncorrected/nFR7N/ |archivedate=2012-01-22 }}</ref><ref name="autogenerated292">Catastrophe: The 100 Greatest Disasters of All Time, Stephen J. Spignesi, Citadel, 2004, pp 292–94</ref>。

2009年1月1日凌晨兩點，[[舊金山灣區捷運|舊金山灣區捷運]]（BART）的數名捷運警察在[[福祿維爾車站|福祿維爾車站]]月台上盤問幾個人。期間白人警員Johannes Mehserle {{le|BART_Police_shooting_of_Oscar_Grant||開槍打死已經趴在地下的黑人青年Oscar Grant III}}。有乘客拍攝到當時情形，但開槍警員沒有被其他同事拉回去調查，反而失蹤。片段被放上分享網站[[Youtube|Youtube]]，激發公憤。一月七日，大批有色人種上街示威，示威最後變成暴動<ref>{{cite news |last=Bulwa |first=Demian |last2=Burress |first2=Charles |last3=Stannard |first3=Matthew B. |last4=Kuruvila |first4=Matthai |title=Protests over BART shooting turn violent |work=San Francisco Chronicle |date=January 8, 2009 |url=http://articles.sfgate.com/2009-01-08/news/17195522_1_bart-police-police-officer-demonstrators |accessdate=June 17, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726043111/http://articles.sfgate.com/2009-01-08/news/17195522_1_bart-police-police-officer-demonstrators |archivedate=2011-07-26 }}</ref>。涉案警員于1月14日被人于內華達州捉回來候審。2010年7月，Jonannes Mehserle被裁定誤殺罪名成立，被判入獄兩年。裁決引發另一次示威<ref>{{cite news |last=MacAskill |first=Ewan |title=Oakland riots after verdict in police shooting of Oscar Grant |work=The Guardian |location=London |date=July 9, 2010 |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2010/jul/09/oakland-riots-oscar-grant-shooting-verdict |accessdate=June 17, 2011 |archive-date=2013-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723164708/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2010/jul/09/oakland-riots-oscar-grant-shooting-verdict |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Richardson |first=Chris |title=Mehserle verdict: Johannes Mehserle sentencing stuns Oscar Grant supporters, sparks riots in Oakland |publisher=The Christian Science Monitor |date=November 5, 2010 |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Justice/2010/1105/Mehserle-verdict-Johannes-Mehserle-sentencing-stuns-Oscar-Grant-supporters-sparks-riots-in-Oakland |accessdate=June 17, 2011 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206053116/https://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Justice/2010/1105/Mehserle-verdict-Johannes-Mehserle-sentencing-stuns-Oscar-Grant-supporters-sparks-riots-in-Oakland |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="behindmurdercharge">{{cite news |last=Bulwa |first=Demian |last2=Buchanan |first2=Wyatt |last3=Yi |first3=Matthew |title=Behind murder charge against ex-BART officer |work=San Francisco Chronicle |date=January 15, 2009 |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2009/01/15/MNJE15A6O2.DTL |accessdate=June 17, 2011 |archive-date=2009-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090415065516/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2009%2F01%2F15%2FMNJE15A6O2.DTL |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="bulwa">{{cite news |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2009/01/30/BABI15KCD5.DTL&type=adfree |title=Skeptical judge grants bail to former BART cop |last=Bulwa |first=Demian |date=January 30, 2009 |work=San Francisco Chronicle |accessdate=June 17, 2011 |archive-date=2009-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203071629/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2009%2F01%2F30%2FBABI15KCD5.DTL&type=adfree |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年3月21日，{{tsl|en|2009 shooting of Oakland police officers||假釋犯Lovelle Mixon}}在街上被截查時開槍打死兩個警察，奧克蘭市警察局立即聯同阿拉米達縣警局（Alameda County Sheriff's Office，ACSO）、加州公路巡邏隊（California Highway Patrol，CHP）和捷運鐵路警察部一齊搜捕。當奧克蘭警察局攻擊小隊來到Mixon藏身處時，Mixon 開槍打死兩個行頭的警長，又打傷了第三個警員；但最後都還是被再後面上來的警員打死了<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nbcbayarea.com/news/local/Two-Officers-Shot-in-Oakland.html |title=Fourth Oakland Police Officer Dies |author=Preuitt, Lori |date=March 23, 2009 |publisher=NBC Bay Area |accessdate=May 5, 2011 |archive-date=2019-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617072155/https://www.nbcbayarea.com/news/local/Two-Officers-Shot-in-Oakland.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

華裔候任市長[[關麗珍|關麗珍]]于2011年1月3日宣誓上任，成為奧克蘭市首位華裔市長和首位女市長<ref>{{cite news |last=Gammon |first=Robert |title=Breaking news: Jean Quan wins mayor's race |publisher=[[East_Bay_Express|East Bay Express]] |date=November 10, 2011 |url=http://www.eastbayexpress.com/92510/archives/2010/11/10/breaking-news-jean-quan-wins-mayors-race |accessdate=October 29, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111212023250/http://www.eastbayexpress.com/92510/archives/2010/11/10/breaking-news-jean-quan-wins-mayors-race |archive-date=2011-12-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2011年10月10日，受「[[佔領華爾街|佔領華爾街行動]]」影響，「佔領行動」來到奧克蘭，變為「佔領奧克蘭行動」（{{tsl|en|Occupy Oakland|}}）。示威者聚集在市政府前的 {{tsl|en|Frank Ogawa|}} 廣場並且紮營露宿<ref name="businessweek">[http://www.businessweek.com/ap/financialnews/D9Q4CNR81.htm Wall Street protesters: We're in for the long haul] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20120525171410/http://www.businessweek.com/ap/financialnews/D9Q4CNR81.htm |date=2012-05-25 }} ''Bloomberg Businessweek''. Accessed: October 3, 2011.</ref><ref name="lessighp">{{cite news|last=Lessig|first=Lawrence|title=#OccupyWallSt, Then #OccupyKSt, Then #OccupyMainSt|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/lawrence-lessig/occupywallst-then-occupyk_b_995547.html|accessdate=October 6, 2011|work=Huffington Post|date=October 5, 2011|authorlink=Lawrence Lessig|archive-date=2019-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190320163759/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/lawrence-lessig/occupywallst-then-occupyk_b_995547.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Bulwa|first=Demian|title=Occupy Oakland looking to expand|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2011/10/18/MNMU1LJ2JA.DTL|accessdate=October 20, 2011|newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle|date=October 19, 2011}}</ref><ref name="CBS San Francisco">{{cite news|title='Occupy Oakland' Encampment Becomes Bustling Community|url=http://sanfrancisco.cbslocal.com/2011/10/20/%E2%80%98occupy-oakland%E2%80%99-encampment-becomes-bustling-community/|accessdate=October 23, 2011|publisher=CBS San Francisco|date=October 20, 2011|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224045126/https://sanfrancisco.cbslocal.com/2011/10/20/%E2%80%98occupy-oakland%E2%80%99-encampment-becomes-bustling-community/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Alston|first=John|title='Occupy Oakland' takes over a second park|url=http://abclocal.go.com/kgo/story?section=news/local/east_bay&id=8396951|accessdate=October 23, 2011|publisher=KGO|date=October 18, 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111019200740/http://abclocal.go.com/kgo/story?section=news%2Flocal%2Feast_bay&id=8396951|archive-date=2011-10-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。「佔領奧克蘭行動」持續到11月中，期間示威者同執法人員爆發多次衝突。例如11月2日，示威者聚集在海港碼頭，執法人員到場驅趕示威者，行動中，兩名示威者重傷<ref>{{cite news|title=Occupy Oakland throng closes down port|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2011/11/03/MN8Q1LPI1J.DTL|accessdate=November 3, 2011|date=November 2, 2011|newspaper=The San Francisco Chronicle|first1=Demian|last1=Bulwa|first2=Matthai|last2=Kuruvila|first3=Kevin|last3=Fagan|archive-date=2011-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111104145051/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2011%2F11%2F03%2FMN8Q1LPI1J.DTL|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於傷者可能因執法人員使用過度武力而受傷，輿論抨擊市政府處理手法。另外有1名示威者被人開槍打死，兇手還未找到<ref name=police_clear>{{cite news|last=Bulwa|first=Demian|title=Police clear Occupy Oakland camps, arrest dozens|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2011/10/25/BAUB1LLTC9.DTL|accessdate=October 25, 2011|newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle|date=October 25, 2011|archive-date=2011-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111025183706/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2011%2F10%2F25%2FBAUB1LLTC9.DTL|dead-url=no}}</ref>。「佔領奧克蘭行動」于11月14日結束<ref>{{cite news|title=Occupy Oakland's cost to city soars to $2.4M|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2011/11/14/BAD91LV10T.DTL|last=Kuruvila|first=Matthai|accessdate=November 15, 2011|date=November 15, 2011|newspaper=The San Francisco Chronicle|archive-date=2011-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111117133130/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2011%2F11%2F14%2FBAD91LV10T.DTL|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年4月2日早晨十點半左右，位於奧克蘭東部的私立大學 Oikos University {{tsl|en|Oikos University shooting||發生兇案}}，韓籍疑凶One L. Goh 在校園開槍射殺了七個人并打傷三個人。案發大約一個鐘頭之後，疑兇向阿拉米逹市警方自首<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-201_162-57408214/fatal-shooting-at-oakland-religious-school |title=7 dead in shooting at Oakland religious school |date=April 2, 2012 |work=CBS News |accessdate=April 3, 2012 |archive-date=2013-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513045636/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-201_162-57408214/fatal-shooting-at-oakland-religious-school |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 地理、氣候 ==
=== 地理 ===
奧克蘭市大約位於北緯37度48分，西經122度15分。總面積為202.4平方公里（78.2平方英里），陸地面積有145.2平方公里（56.1平方英里），水面積是57.2平方公里（22.1平方英里）。沿海灣大部分地方為平地，再深入內陸就是山。粗略可以將奧克蘭分做{{tsl|en|North Oakland, California||北}}、{{tsl|en|East Oakland, Oakland, California||東}}、{{tsl|en|West Oakland||西}}、和中四個區，另外還有[[Lake_Merritt|湖邊]]、山邊等等小區<ref>{{cite web |title=Oakland and Alameda Waterfront Parks |publisher=Waterfront Action, Inc. |date=April 19, 2011 |url=http://www.waterfrontaction.org/map/legend_parks.htm |accessdate=October 29, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111002072607/http://www.waterfrontaction.org/map/legend_parks.htm |archive-date=2011-10-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2011/07/19/BUUK1KCC67.DTL#ixzz1SfOLM9sW |title=S.F., Oakland in top 10 most walkable U.S. cities |author=Said, Carolyn |date=July 20, 2011 |work=San Francisco Chronicle |accessdate=August 8, 2011 |archive-date=2011-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110919020322/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2011%2F07%2F19%2FBUUK1KCC67.DTL#ixzz1SfOLM9sW |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

由於位於正聖安德烈亞斯斷層（San Andreas Fault）上面<ref>{{cite web |url=http://seismo.berkeley.edu/annual_report/ar98_99/node22.html |title=Modeling surface creep on the Hayward fault using rate-and-state friction |first1=David |last1=Schmidt |first2=Roland |last2=Bürgmann |year=1999 |work=The Berkeley Seismological Laboratory |publisher=The Regents of the University of California |accessdate=August 8, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927211802/http://seismo.berkeley.edu/annual_report/ar98_99/node22.html |archive-date=2011-09-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，奧克蘭同區內其他城市一樣，會受地震威脅。

=== 氣候 ===
奧克蘭夏天乾燥炎熱但冬天潮濕寒冷。日間氣溫可以低至華氏40度（攝氏7度）高至80度（攝氏25度）。降雨量有4.85吋至0.1吋左右<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oaklandchamber.com/relocation/facts.asp |title=Relocation information: Oakland Facts |publisher=Chamber of Commerce |accessdate=July 13, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110903163216/http://www.oaklandchamber.com/relocation/facts.asp |archivedate=2011年9月3日 }} As published in 1993 by Rand McNally.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wrcc.dri.edu/cgi-bin/cliMAIN.pl?ca6332 |title=Oakland, California – Climate Summary |publisher=Wrcc.dri.edu |accessdate=April 19, 2012 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308050119/https://wrcc.dri.edu/cgi-bin/cliMAIN.pl?ca6332 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

